					<description><![CDATA[<p>What's a good conversion rate? It depends on your industry and where you're advertising, but we've got the data in this complete conversion rate benchmarks breakdown!</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/conversion-rate-benchmarks">Conversion Rate Benchmarks for YOUR Industry (Exclusive Data!)</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
