<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/facebook-ads-benchmarks-2025">Facebook Ads Benchmarks 2025: NEW Data, Trends, &#038; Insights for Your Industry</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
