<div id="2025-meta-leads-benchmarks"></div>
<h2>Facebook ads benchmarks: Leads campaigns</h2>
<p>Facebook ads campaigns using the leads objective actively optimize how your ads are served for the most leads possible.</p>
<p>To run Facebook leads campaigns on Meta, you‚Äôll have to <span>create <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/facebook-lead-ads/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Facebook Lead Ads</a></span>, which allow users to become leads with your business directly from the platform.</p>
<p><img decoding="async" src="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/2025-facebook-benchmarks-leads-scaled.webp" alt="2025 facebook ads benchmarks - leads objective chart" width="2560" height="1616" class="aligncenter wp-image-93929 size-full" srcset="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/2025-facebook-benchmarks-leads-scaled.webp 2560w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/2025-facebook-benchmarks-leads-1280x808.webp 1280w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/2025-facebook-benchmarks-leads-980x619.webp 980w, https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/2025-facebook-benchmarks-leads-480x303.webp 480w" sizes="(min-width: 0px) and (max-width: 480px) 480px, (min-width: 481px) and (max-width: 980px) 980px, (min-width: 981px) and (max-width: 1280px) 1280px, (min-width: 1281px) 2560px, 100vw" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.wordstream.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/2025-facebook-benchmarks-leads-scaled.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Click to enlarge</em></a></p>
<p>We‚Äôve included conversion rate and cost per lead as part of these benchmarks since this objective is optimized to <a href="https://localiq.com/blog/lead-generation-ideas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">drive leads</a> and conversions.</p>
<div id="facebook-leads-ctr"></div>
<h3>Average click-through rate for leads campaigns</h3>
<p>A high click-through rate on Facebook leads campaigns tends to equate to high-quality ad copy and creative elements. When your Facebook Lead Ads are effective at driving clicks, it means your ads are compelling enough to draw people in and become leads with your business. So, naturally, click-through tends to be prioritized by businesses looking to generate more leads through Meta Ads.</p>
<p><strong>The average click-through rate in Facebook ads for leads campaigns across all industries is 2.59%.</strong> This is about the same as last year‚Äôs average of 2.58%.</p>
