					<description><![CDATA[<p>Start building out your Google Ads Performance Max strategy with this complete walkthrough of how PMax works to grow your business across channels. </p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/performance-max">What Is Google Ads Performance Max &#038; How Does It Work?</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
